title: Serious Sam TSE [2014 MultiPlayer Edition]
description:
If you haven't heard, GameSpy's Master Servers will be shut down permanently on May 31st, 2014.
FYI: The Master Server collects information about currently active game servers and sends your game browser a list of these servers so that you can choose one to play on. This is what allows players to find each other and play together.
After May 31st you will no longer be able to find any servers to play on through GameSpy (the in-game server browser). However, thanks to enterprising individuals in the Serious Sam community, there is now an alternative Master Server you can use.

25-07-2014
RIP GameSpy 

This version of game using alternetive master server.
Enjoy!
